# NovaKur Theme — Architecture Audit Report

> **Comparing:** [novakur-theme-architecture.md](file:///Users/hilalahamd/MyRestProjects/OpenCartProject/OpenCartThemes/docs/novakur-theme-architecture.md) vs. actual project files  
> **Date:** March 9, 2026

---

## Overall Verdict

The **directory structure and file scaffolding match the architecture plan very well**. All planned folders and files exist. However, **the majority of components are empty stubs/placeholders** — only about 30–35% of the components have real, working implementations. The project has a solid skeleton but needs significant work to be fully implemented.

---

## ✅ What's Correctly In Place

### Directory Structure
The architecture calls for a component-based file structure. The project follows this:

| Architecture Plan | Actual Project | ✅/❌ |
|---|---|---|
| `template/layout/` | `template/component/layout/` | ✅ (slightly different path, uses `component/` parent) |
| `template/ui/` | `template/component/ui/` | ✅ |
| `template/product/` | `template/component/commerce/` | ✅ (renamed `product` → `commerce`) |
| `template/sections/` | `template/component/sections/` | ✅ |
| `template/pages/` | `template/common/` + `template/product/` + `template/account/` + etc. | ✅ (uses OpenCart's native routing structure) |
| `stylesheet/tokens/` | `assets/scss/abstracts/` | ✅ (renamed `tokens` → `abstracts`) |
| `stylesheet/components/` | `assets/scss/layout/` + `ui/` + `commerce/` + `sections/` | ✅ (more granular, actually better) |
| `javascript/modules/` | `assets/js/layout/` + `ui/` + `commerce/` + `sections/` | ✅ (same modular approach) |

### File Count Match

| Category | Architecture Plan | Actually Created | Match |
|---|---|---|---|
| Layout components | 7 files | 7 files | ✅ 100% |
| UI components | 5 listed (+ implied) | 11 files | ✅ Exceeds plan |
| Commerce/Product components | 10 core files | 10 files | ✅ 100% |
| Section modules | 8 listed | 9 files | ✅ 100% |
| Page templates | 5+ listed | 7+ templates | ✅ |
| SCSS files | ~15 listed | 52 files total | ✅ Exceeds plan |
| JS modules | 6 listed | 11 files total | ✅ Exceeds plan |

### Design Tokens / Variables
The architecture specifies design tokens (`#2563EB` primary, `#1E3A8A` deep, `#0F172A` text, `#FFFFFF` background). The actual [_variables.scss](file:///Users/hilalahamd/MyRestProjects/OpenCartProject/OpenCartThemes/catalog/view/assets/scss/abstracts/_variables.scss) has:
- ✅ `--nk-primary: #2563eb` — matches
- ✅ `--nk-secondary: #1e3a8a` — matches
- ✅ `--nk-text: #0f172a` — matches
- ✅ `--nk-bg: #ffffff` — matches
- ✅ CSS custom properties used (overridable per variant as required)

### Main Entry Files
- ✅ [main.scss](file:///Users/hilalahamd/MyRestProjects/OpenCartProject/OpenCartThemes/catalog/view/assets/scss/main.scss) — properly imports all component partials in the correct order
- ✅ [main.js](file:///Users/hilalahamd/MyRestProjects/OpenCartProject/OpenCartThemes/catalog/view/assets/js/main.js) — properly imports and initializes all JS modules on `DOMContentLoaded`

