## ❌ Gaps & Missing Items

### 1. Missing Architecture Features (Not Built Yet)
- **Announcement Bar** — No promotional strip above header
- **Mega Menu** — No dropdown category navigation
- **Mobile Nav Drawer** — No off-canvas mobile navigation
- **Rating Stars** — No star rating component
- **Search Input** — No predictive search
- **Quantity Selector** — No +/- quantity control (stub only)
- **Wishlist Button** — No wishlist functionality
- **Benefits Bar** — No trust signal strip (Free Shipping, etc.)
- **Newsletter Signup** — No email capture form
- **Promo Banners** — No promotional image banners
- **Related Products Carousel** — No related products on PDP

### 2. Design System Gaps
- ⚠️ Variables file is minimal (6 variables). Architecture specifies full token system for spacing, radius, shadows, typography scale
- ⚠️ No dark mode implementation yet (`dark:` class variants required)
- ⚠️ No Inter font import (architecture specifies Inter as the base font)
- ⚠️ No Material Symbols icon font import

### 3. Variant System Not Started
- Architecture specifies 3 header variants (v1, v2, v3-glass) — only 1 exists
- Architecture specifies 3 footer variants — only 1 exists
- Architecture specifies 4 product card variants — only 1 exists (standard)
- Architecture specifies 2 hero banner variants — only 1 exists

### 4. Missing Architectural Components Not In File Tree
- `ui/ToastNotification` — No file exists at all
- `ui/ModalOverlay` — No file exists at all
- `product/RecentlyViewed` — No file exists at all

---

## 🎯 Recommendations (Priority Order)

1. **HIGH:** Implement `mobile_nav_drawer` — critical for mobile users
2. **HIGH:** Implement `mega_menu` — critical for desktop navigation
3. **HIGH:** Implement `announcement_bar` — visible on every page
4. **HIGH:** Implement `rating_stars` + `quantity_selector` — core commerce UX
5. **MEDIUM:** Implement `benefits_bar` + `newsletter_signup` — trust & conversion
6. **MEDIUM:** Implement `wishlist_button` + `stock_badge` + `discount_badge`
7. **MEDIUM:** Expand design tokens ([_variables.scss](file:///Users/hilalahamd/MyRestProjects/OpenCartProject/OpenCartThemes/catalog/view/assets/scss/abstracts/_variables.scss)) with full spacing/radius/shadow/typography scale
8. **MEDIUM:** Add Inter font + Material Symbols icon imports
9. **LOW:** Build variant system for headers, footers, and product cards
10. **LOW:** Implement dark mode support
